'''Jal Shey Neophyte armor''' was, as the name suggests, used by the [[Jal Shey]] [[Jal Shey Neophyte|neophytes]]. The neophytes were those who had just begun their life-long quest to understand the intellectual nature of [[The Force/Legends|the Force]]. Their [[Armor/Legends|armor]] was very lightweight and, as such, did not encumber the wearer of the ability to utilize [[Force power/Legends|Force powers]]. This armor saw use in the time around the [[Jedi Civil War]].

